  dungeons:
  - dungeonName: 'The Blazing Beast '
    dungeonDescription: Looks like you'll be able to leave this case soon, but there
      seems to be something sinister awaiting for you at the end. (Dialogue)
  - dungeonName: 'The Thief''s Hideout '
    dungeonDescription: You've come far, but there's still no exit in site. There
