  - dungeonName: Wielder of Fire
    dungeonDescription: 'Continue deeper into the Cave of Flames. Beings who control
      fire are waiting ahead. '
  - dungeonName: Cave of Dancing Flames
    dungeonDescription: The magma flowing within this cave give off and intense heat.
      The enemies in this cave have the power of fire.
